extends java.util.Observable
    This class represents a warehouse. It keeps track of all resources in the hospital including food, plaster, medication,...

    • Constructor Detail

      • Warehouse

        public Warehouse(HospitalDate startDate)
          throws InvalidHospitalDateException
        Default constructor. Fields will be initialised. Also the warehouse stock will be filled up completely with everything.
        Parameters:
        startDate - The date that this warehouse starts existing on. Will be used to calculate the difference in time between the new system time and the current system time, should the time advance.
        Throws:
        InvalidHospitalDateException
